{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"0000000000000001","type":"text","x":0,"y":-400,"width":2400,"height":150,"text":"# 🚀 Claude Code 从入门到精通\n\n**终端中的超级 AI 编程助手 | Agentic Coding 的标杆产品**\n\n> \"Most software engineers are seriously sleeping on how good LLM agents are right now, especially something like Claude Code.\"\n> \n> 代码、配置、工作流全部可定制，打造属于你的 AI 编程超级队友","color":"5"},
		{"id":"0000000000000002","type":"group","x":-50,"y":-200,"width":800,"height":550,"label":"📥 第一章：安装与配置","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000003","type":"text","x":0,"y":-150,"width":350,"height":200,"text":"### 🔧 安装方式\n\n**macOS / Linux (推荐)**\n```shell\ncurl -fsSL https://claude.ai/install.sh | bash\n```\n\n**Homebrew**\n```shell\nbrew install --cask claude-code\n```\n\n**旧版 npm (已废弃)**\n```shell\nnpm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000004","type":"text","x":400,"y":-150,"width":350,"height":200,"text":"### 🖥️ 多环境使用\n\n**OrbStack 容器**\n```shell\norb -m ubuntu -u root\n```\n\n**mise 环境管理**\n```shell\ncurl https://mise.run | sh\nmise use node\nnpm install -g @anthropic-ai/claude-code\n```\n\n**Windows**: 使用 WSL2"},
		{"id":"0000000000000005","type":"text","x":0,"y":70,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### 📁 CLAUDE.md 项目记忆\n\n**位置优先级**:\n1. `.claude/CLAUDE.md`\n2. `./CLAUDE.md` (项目根目录)\n3. `~/.claude/CLAUDE.md` (全局)\n\n**推荐内容**:\n- 常用 bash 命令\n- 代码风格指南\n- 测试指令\n- 仓库规范\n- 环境配置\n\n**自动生成**: `/init` 命令","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000006","type":"text","x":400,"y":70,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### ⚙️ settings.json 配置\n\n**位置**: `.claude/settings.json`\n\n```json\n{\n  \"model\": \"claude-sonnet-4\",\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"Stop\": [{\n      \"hooks\": [{\n        \"type\": \"command\",\n        \"command\": \"afplay notification.mp3\"\n      }]\n    }]\n  },\n  \"permissions\": {\n    \"allow\": [\"Bash(ls:*)\", \"Edit\"],\n    \"deny\": [\"Bash(rm:*)\"]\n  }\n}\n```","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000007","type":"group","x":800,"y":-200,"width":800,"height":550,"label":"⌨️ 第二章：核心命令与快捷键","color":"2"},
		{"id":"0000000000000008","type":"text","x":850,"y":-150,"width":350,"height":220,"text":"### 📋 常用斜杠命令\n\n| 命令 | 功能 |\n|------|------|\n| `/init` | 生成 CLAUDE.md |\n| `/compact` | 压缩上下文 |\n| `/clear` | 清空上下文 |\n| `/ide` | 连接 IDE |\n| `/permissions` | 权限管理 |\n| `/export` | 导出对话 |\n| `/agent` | 子代理模式 |\n| `/plugin` | 插件管理 |"},
		{"id":"0000000000000009","type":"text","x":1250,"y":-150,"width":350,"height":220,"text":"### ⚡ 快捷键\n\n| 快捷键 | 功能 |\n|--------|------|\n| `Ctrl+R` | 展开收缩内容 |\n| `Shift+Tab` | 切换 Plan Mode |\n| `Escape` | 中断当前操作 |\n| `Escape×2` | 回退历史编辑 |\n| `\\ + Enter` | 换行输入 |\n| `#` | 记忆模式 |\n| `!` | 执行命令模式 |"},
		{"id":"0000000000000010","type":"text","x":850,"y":90,"width":350,"height":230,"text":"### 🧠 思考强度控制\n\n**触发 Extended Thinking**:\n\n| 关键词 | 强度 |\n|--------|------|\n| `think` | 基础 |\n| `think hard` | 中等 |\n| `think harder` | 高 |\n| `ultrathink` | 最高 |\n| `ultrawork` | 最高 |\n\n每级分配更多思考预算","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000011","type":"text","x":1250,"y":90,"width":350,"height":230,"text":"### 🎯 权限模式\n\n**YOLO 模式 (危险)**\n```shell\nclaude --dangerously-skip-permissions\n```\n\n**精细化权限**\n```\n/permissions\n```\n\n规则语法:\n- `Edit` - 允许编辑\n- `Bash(git commit:*)` - 允许 git\n- `Bash(rm:*)` - 禁止删除","color":"1"},
		{"id":"0000000000000012","type":"group","x":1650,"y":-200,"width":800,"height":550,"label":"🔌 第三章：MCP 与外部集成","color":"6"},
		{"id":"0000000000000013","type":"text","x":1700,"y":-150,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### 🌐 MCP 架构\n\n```\n┌─────────────┐\n│ Claude Code │\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │ MCP Protocol\n┌──────▼──────┐\n│  MCP Server │ (本地桥接)\n└──────┬──────┘\n       │ API Call\n┌──────▼──────┐\n│ External API│\n│ JIRA/GitHub │\n└─────────────┘\n```\n\n**配置文件**: `.mcp.json`"},
		{"id":"0000000000000014","type":"text","x":2100,"y":-150,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### 📦 常用 MCP 服务器\n\n**Issue Tracking**\n- `@anthropic/mcp-jira`\n- `@anthropic/mcp-linear`\n\n**Code & DevOps**\n- `@anthropic/mcp-github`\n- `@anthropic/mcp-sentry`\n\n**Communication**\n- `@anthropic/mcp-slack`\n\n**Database**\n- `@anthropic/mcp-postgres`\n\n**Browser**\n- `@playwright/mcp`"},
		{"id":"0000000000000015","type":"text","x":1700,"y":120,"width":750,"height":200,"text":"### 📝 MCP 配置示例\n\n```json\n{\n  \"mcpServers\": {\n    \"jira\": {\n      \"type\": \"stdio\",\n      \"command\": \"npx\",\n      \"args\": [\"-y\", \"@anthropic/mcp-jira\"],\n      \"env\": {\n        \"JIRA_HOST\": \"${JIRA_HOST}\",\n        \"JIRA_EMAIL\": \"${JIRA_EMAIL}\",\n        \"JIRA_API_TOKEN\": \"${JIRA_API_TOKEN}\"\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n```","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000016","type":"group","x":-50,"y":400,"width":1250,"height":600,"label":"📚 第四章：Skills 技能系统","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000017","type":"text","x":0,"y":450,"width":400,"height":250,"text":"### 🎓 什么是 Skills\n\nSkills 是教会 Claude 项目特定模式的 Markdown 文档\n\n**位置**: `.claude/skills/{name}/SKILL.md`\n\n**作用**:\n- 代码风格规范\n- 测试模式\n- API 设计规范\n- 组件库使用方式\n- 调试方法论\n\n**核心理念**: 让 Claude 生成的代码开箱即用，符合团队规范"},
		{"id":"0000000000000018","type":"text","x":450,"y":450,"width":400,"height":250,"text":"### 📄 SKILL.md 格式\n\n```markdown\n---\nname: testing-patterns\ndescription: Jest 测试模式\nallowed-tools: Read, Grep, Glob\nmodel: claude-sonnet-4\n---\n\n# Testing Patterns\n\n## When to Use\n- 编写测试时\n- TDD 工作流\n\n## Core Patterns\n### AAA 模式\nArrange → Act → Assert\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000019","type":"text","x":900,"y":450,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### 🏷️ Frontmatter 字段\n\n| 字段 | 必填 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `name` | ✅ | 小写+连字符 |\n| `description` | ✅ | 触发描述 |\n| `allowed-tools` | ❌ | 允许工具 |\n| `model` | ❌ | 指定模型 |\n\n**最佳实践**:\n- 保持 < 500 行\n- 包含代码示例\n- 写明反模式"},
		{"id":"0000000000000020","type":"text","x":0,"y":720,"width":600,"height":250,"text":"### 🎯 示例 Skills\n\n| Skill | 用途 |\n|-------|------|\n| `testing-patterns` | TDD、工厂函数、Mock |\n| `systematic-debugging` | 四阶段调试法 |\n| `react-ui-patterns` | Loading/Error/Empty 状态 |\n| `graphql-schema` | 查询、变更、Codegen |\n| `core-components` | 设计系统、Token |\n| `formik-patterns` | 表单处理、验证 |","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000021","type":"text","x":650,"y":720,"width":600,"height":250,"text":"### 🔍 Skill 自动评估系统\n\n**触发时机**: `UserPromptSubmit` Hook\n\n**分析维度**:\n1. **Keywords**: 简单词匹配\n2. **Patterns**: 正则匹配\n3. **File Paths**: 文件路径提取\n4. **Intent**: 意图检测\n\n**置信度评分**:\n- keyword: 2分\n- pathPattern: 4分\n- directoryMatch: 5分\n- intentPattern: 4分","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000022","type":"group","x":1250,"y":400,"width":1200,"height":600,"label":"🤖 第五章：Agents 与 Commands","color":"1"},
		{"id":"0000000000000023","type":"text","x":1300,"y":450,"width":550,"height":250,"text":"### 🕵️ Agents 专项助手\n\n**位置**: `.claude/agents/{name}.md`\n\n**格式**:\n```markdown\n---\nname: code-reviewer\ndescription: 代码审查专家\nmodel: opus\n---\n\n# Agent System Prompt\n\n你是一位资深代码审查员...\n\n## 审查流程\n1. 运行 `git diff`\n2. 应用审查清单\n3. 提供反馈\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000024","type":"text","x":1900,"y":450,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 📋 示例 Agents\n\n| Agent | 用途 |\n|-------|------|\n| `code-reviewer` | 综合代码审查 |\n| `github-workflow` | Git 操作专家 |\n| `security-auditor` | 安全审计 |\n| `performance-optimizer` | 性能优化 |\n| `documentation-writer` | 文档编写 |\n\n**触发**: Claude 自动识别或手动调用"},
		{"id":"0000000000000025","type":"text","x":1300,"y":720,"width":550,"height":250,"text":"### ⚡ Custom Commands\n\n**位置**: `.claude/commands/{name}.md`\n\n**调用**: `/project:{name}` 或 `/{name}`\n\n**变量**:\n- `$ARGUMENTS` - 全部参数\n- `$1`, `$2`, `$3` - 位置参数\n\n**内联 Bash**:\n```\n当前分支: !`git branch --show-current`\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000026","type":"text","x":1900,"y":720,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 📋 示例 Commands\n\n| Command | 用途 |\n|---------|------|\n| `/onboard` | 深度任务探索 |\n| `/ticket` | JIRA 工作流 |\n| `/pr-review` | PR 审查 |\n| `/pr-summary` | 生成 PR 描述 |\n| `/code-quality` | 质量检查 |\n| `/docs-sync` | 文档同步 |\n\n**示例**: `/ticket PROJ-123`"},
		{"id":"0000000000000027","type":"group","x":-50,"y":1050,"width":1600,"height":600,"label":"🔄 第六章：Hooks 自动化系统","color":"2"},
		{"id":"0000000000000028","type":"text","x":0,"y":1100,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 🎣 Hook 事件类型\n\n| 事件 | 触发时机 | 用例 |\n|------|----------|------|\n| `PreToolUse` | 工具执行前 | 阻止危险操作 |\n| `PostToolUse` | 工具执行后 | 自动格式化 |\n| `UserPromptSubmit` | 用户提交 | 添加上下文 |\n| `Stop` | Agent 结束 | 播放通知音 |\n| `Notification` | 通知时 | 桌面提醒 |"},
		{"id":"0000000000000029","type":"text","x":550,"y":1100,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 📤 Hook 响应格式\n\n```json\n{\n  \"block\": true,\n  \"message\": \"阻止原因\",\n  \"feedback\": \"非阻塞反馈\",\n  \"suppressOutput\": true,\n  \"continue\": false\n}\n```\n\n**Exit Codes**:\n- `0` - 成功\n- `2` - 阻塞错误 (仅 PreToolUse)\n- 其他 - 非阻塞错误"},
		{"id":"0000000000000030","type":"text","x":1100,"y":1100,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 🛡️ 安全 Hook 示例\n\n**禁止在 main 分支编辑**:\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"PreToolUse\": [{\n      \"matcher\": \"Edit|Write\",\n      \"hooks\": [{\n        \"type\": \"command\",\n        \"command\": \"[ \\\"$(git branch)\\\" != \\\"main\\\" ]\",\n        \"timeout\": 5\n      }]\n    }]\n  }\n}\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000031","type":"text","x":0,"y":1370,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 🔔 通知音效 Hook\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"Stop\": [{\n      \"hooks\": [{\n        \"type\": \"command\",\n        \"command\": \"afplay ~/Sounds/done.mp3\"\n      }]\n    }],\n    \"Notification\": [{\n      \"hooks\": [{\n        \"type\": \"command\",\n        \"command\": \"afplay ~/Sounds/notify.mp3\"\n      }]\n    }]\n  }\n}\n```","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000032","type":"text","x":550,"y":1370,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### ✨ 自动格式化 Hook\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"PostToolUse\": [{\n      \"matcher\": \"Edit|Write\",\n      \"hooks\": [{\n        \"type\": \"command\",\n        \"command\": \"prettier --write $FILE\"\n      }]\n    }]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**应用场景**:\n- 代码格式化\n- 运行 linter\n- 类型检查","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000033","type":"text","x":1100,"y":1370,"width":500,"height":250,"text":"### 🧪 测试触发 Hook\n\n```json\n{\n  \"hooks\": {\n    \"PostToolUse\": [{\n      \"matcher\": \"Edit\",\n      \"hooks\": [{\n        \"type\": \"command\",\n        \"command\": \"if [[ $FILE == *.test.* ]]; then npm test -- $FILE; fi\"\n      }]\n    }]\n  }\n}\n```\n\n测试文件修改后自动运行测试","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000034","type":"group","x":1600,"y":1050,"width":850,"height":600,"label":"🔧 第七章：GitHub Actions 自动化","color":"5"},
		{"id":"0000000000000035","type":"text","x":1650,"y":1100,"width":750,"height":250,"text":"### 🤖 PR 自动审查\n\n```yaml\nname: PR - Claude Code Review\non:\n  pull_request:\n    types: [opened, synchronize]\n  issue_comment:\n    types: [created]\n\njobs:\n  review:\n    runs-on: ubuntu-latest\n    steps:\n      - uses: anthropics/claude-code-action@beta\n        with:\n          anthropic_api_key: ${{ secrets.ANTHROPIC_API_KEY }}\n          model: claude-opus-4-5-20251101\n          prompt: \"Review this PR...\"\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000036","type":"text","x":1650,"y":1370,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### 📅 定时任务\n\n| 工作流 | 周期 | 用途 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| Code Quality | 每周日 | 随机审查目录 |\n| Docs Sync | 每月1号 | 文档对齐 |\n| Dependency Audit | 每两周 | 依赖更新 |\n\n**预估月成本**: $10-50\n(取决于 PR 数量)"},
		{"id":"0000000000000037","type":"text","x":2050,"y":1370,"width":350,"height":250,"text":"### 💰 成本估算\n\n| 工作流 | 频率 | 成本 |\n|--------|------|------|\n| PR Review | 每 PR | $0.05-0.50 |\n| Docs Sync | 每月 | $0.50-2.00 |\n| Dep Audit | 双周 | $0.20-1.00 |\n| Quality | 每周 | $1.00-5.00 |\n\n**节省**: 大量人工审查时间"},
		{"id":"0000000000000038","type":"group","x":-50,"y":1700,"width":1250,"height":550,"label":"🎯 第八章：最佳实践工作流","color":"4"},
		{"id":"0000000000000039","type":"text","x":0,"y":1750,"width":400,"height":220,"text":"### 🔄 Explore → Plan → Code → Commit\n\n1. **探索**: 阅读相关文件\n   - 告诉它\"不要写代码\"\n   - 使用 subagent 深入调查\n\n2. **计划**: 让 Claude 制定方案\n   - 使用 \"think\" 触发深度思考\n   - 创建计划文档\n\n3. **编码**: 实现方案\n4. **提交**: 生成 PR"},
		{"id":"0000000000000040","type":"text","x":450,"y":1750,"width":400,"height":220,"text":"### 🧪 TDD 工作流\n\n1. **写测试**: 基于预期输入输出\n   - 明确告知是 TDD\n   - 避免 mock 实现\n\n2. **验证失败**: 确认测试失败\n3. **提交测试**: 满意后提交\n4. **写代码**: 让测试通过\n   - 不修改测试\n   - 迭代直到全部通过\n5. **提交代码**"},
		{"id":"0000000000000041","type":"text","x":900,"y":1750,"width":350,"height":220,"text":"### 🖼️ 视觉迭代工作流\n\n1. 给 Claude 截图能力\n   - Puppeteer MCP\n   - iOS Simulator MCP\n\n2. 提供设计稿\n   - 拖放图片\n   - 粘贴截图\n\n3. 实现 → 截图 → 对比 → 迭代\n4. 满意后提交"},
		{"id":"0000000000000042","type":"text","x":0,"y":1990,"width":400,"height":230,"text":"### 🎫 Ticket 工作流\n\n```\n/ticket PROJ-123\n```\n\n1. 从 JIRA 获取 ticket 详情\n2. 读取验收标准\n3. 搜索相关代码\n4. 创建功能分支\n5. 实现功能\n6. 更新 JIRA 状态\n7. 创建 PR 并链接 ticket","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000043","type":"text","x":450,"y":1990,"width":400,"height":230,"text":"### 🔀 Multi-Claude 工作流\n\n**方式一: 写/审分离**\n1. Claude A 写代码\n2. `/clear` 或新终端\n3. Claude B 审查代码\n4. Claude C 根据反馈修改\n\n**方式二: Git Worktrees**\n```shell\ngit worktree add ../feature-a\ncd ../feature-a && claude\n```","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000044","type":"text","x":900,"y":1990,"width":350,"height":230,"text":"### 📊 Headless 自动化\n\n**批量处理**:\n```shell\nclaude -p \"migrate foo.py\" \\\n  --allowedTools Edit \\\n  --output-format json\n```\n\n**流水线集成**:\n```shell\nclaude -p \"analyze\" --json \\\n  | your_command\n```","color":"3"},
		{"id":"0000000000000045","type":"group","x":1250,"y":1700,"width":1200,"height":550,"label":"💡 第九章：高级技巧与生态","color":"6"},
		{"id":"0000000000000046","type":"text","x":1300,"y":1750,"width":550,"height":220,"text":"### 🎮 Vibe Coding\n\n**定义**: Claude Code + 语音输入 + 纯自然语言\n\n全自动实现功能，很少看代码，只看最终效果\n\n**三员大将**:\n```shell\nclaude --dangerously-skip-permissions\ncodex --sandbox workspace-write --ask-for-approval never\ngemini -m gemini-3-flash-preview --yolo\n```\n\n**安全措施**: `brew install trash && alias rm='trash'`"},
		{"id":"0000000000000047","type":"text","x":1900,"y":1750,"width":500,"height":220,"text":"### 🔌 第三方工具生态\n\n**用量监控**\n- `ccusage` / `claude-code-monitor`\n\n**状态栏**\n- `CCometixLine` (Rust)\n\n**音效**\n- `zelda-claude-code`\n\n**可视化界面**\n- `Claudia`\n\n**路由器**\n- `claude-code-router`"},
		{"id":"0000000000000048","type":"text","x":1300,"y":1990,"width":550,"height":230,"text":"### 🔗 IDE 集成\n\n**VS Code / Cursor**:\n1. 安装 Claude Code 插件\n2. 终端输入 `/ide`\n\n**优势**:\n- IDE 选中代码 → Claude 感知\n- Claude 改动 → IDE 显示 diff\n- 双向实时同步\n\n**Plan Mode**: `Shift+Tab` 切换"},
		{"id":"0000000000000049","type":"text","x":1900,"y":1990,"width":500,"height":230,"text":"### 📖 LSP 实时智能\n\n**启用**:\n```json\n{\n  \"enabledPlugins\": {\n    \"typescript-lsp@claude-plugins-official\": true,\n    \"pyright-lsp@claude-plugins-official\": true\n  }\n}\n```\n\n**能力**:\n- 实时错误诊断\n- 类型信息\n- 代码导航\n- 智能补全"},
		{"id":"0000000000000050","type":"group","x":-50,"y":2300,"width":2500,"height":350,"label":"📁 完整目录结构","color":"5"},
		{"id":"0000000000000051","type":"text","x":0,"y":2350,"width":800,"height":270,"text":"### 📂 项目配置结构\n\n```\nyour-project/\n├── CLAUDE.md                    # 项目记忆 (可选位置)\n├── .mcp.json                    # MCP 服务器配置\n├── .claude/\n│   ├── settings.json            # Hooks, 环境, 权限\n│   ├── settings.local.json      # 个人覆盖 (gitignore)\n│   ├── settings.md              # Hook 文档\n│   ├── .gitignore\n│   ├── agents/                  # 自定义 AI Agents\n│   │   └── code-reviewer.md\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000052","type":"text","x":850,"y":2350,"width":800,"height":270,"text":"```\n│   ├── commands/                # 斜杠命令\n│   │   ├── onboard.md\n│   │   ├── pr-review.md\n│   │   └── ticket.md\n│   ├── hooks/                   # Hook 脚本\n│   │   ├── skill-eval.sh\n│   │   ├── skill-eval.js\n│   │   └── skill-rules.json\n│   └── skills/                  # 领域知识\n│       ├── README.md\n│       ├── testing-patterns/\n│       │   └── SKILL.md\n│       └── react-ui-patterns/\n│           └── SKILL.md\n```"},
		{"id":"0000000000000053","type":"text","x":1700,"y":2350,"width":700,"height":270,"text":"```\n└── .github/\n    └── workflows/\n        ├── pr-claude-code-review.yml\n        ├── scheduled-claude-code-docs-sync.yml\n        ├── scheduled-claude-code-quality.yml\n        └── scheduled-claude-code-dependency-audit.yml\n```\n\n**版本控制**:\n- ✅ 提交: settings.json, agents, commands, skills\n- ❌ 忽略: settings.local.json, CLAUDE.local.md"},
		{"id":"0000000000000054","type":"group","x":-50,"y":2700,"width":2500,"height":250,"label":"📚 相关资源链接","color":"3"},
